Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.20,0:23:32.43,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}还曾以为自己不再恋爱
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.65,0:23:35.79,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}喜欢上人的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.02,0:23:39.65,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}似乎难以用道理言表
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.91,0:23:45.27,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}我啊  恋爱了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.34,0:23:52.88,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}再一次  重新开始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.23,0:23:58.95,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}淡淡甜美的青葱岁月
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.62,0:24:06.31,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}不可再来的瞬间与感触
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.88,0:24:11.64,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}纵然已经消逝
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.32,0:24:19.62,edcn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur2}仍珍藏在我的心中的
